00:01:52.640 --> 00:01:53.880
When did you get back?

00:01:54.760 --> 00:01:56.040
Just recently.

00:01:56.940 --> 00:01:58.060
Where are you planning to stay?

00:01:58.660 --> 00:02:00.020
Here, of course.

00:02:06.340 --> 00:02:07.980
You're hiring a male domestic helper?

00:02:10.780 --> 00:02:12.220
