00:02:30.200 --> 00:02:31.660
Why do I have to?

00:02:31.900 --> 00:02:33.040
What did my brother do to you?

00:02:33.600 --> 00:02:34.860
He groped me! He even pinched...

00:02:34.860 --> 00:02:36.640
You're wasting my time with that tiny thing.

00:02:36.640 --> 00:02:38.180
What? Tiny thing?

00:02:38.340 --> 00:02:40.340
He tried to r*pe and then k*ll me!

00:02:40.440 --> 00:02:41.580
Are you a girl?

00:02:42.620 --> 00:02:43.700
