00:02:46.940 --> 00:02:48.440
Do not try to cross the line.

00:02:56.920 --> 00:02:58.080
This kid!

00:03:00.220 --> 00:03:01.540
He's kinda interesting, huh?

00:03:02.280 --> 00:03:04.180
Perverse, stubborn,

00:03:04.660 --> 00:03:06.720
