00:03:19.220 --> 00:03:21.140
You'll find him interesting.

00:03:27.440 --> 00:03:28.680
How are your legs?

00:03:28.960 --> 00:03:30.480
Are they hurt?

00:03:33.100 --> 00:03:34.680
I can walk normally.

00:03:38.280 --> 00:03:40.000
I think you need physical therapy.

00:03:40.800 --> 00:03:42.860
It's painful enough for the eyes.

00:03:45.960 --> 00:03:47.040
I know.

00:03:48.180 --> 00:03:49.320
Have you eaten?

00:03:49.700 --> 00:03:50.680
No, I haven't.

00:03:51.300 --> 00:03:53.280
I planned to eat at the restaurant.

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:55.800
You should go early. Take your time.

00:03:57.960 --> 00:03:59.180
Then, I'll go now.

00:04:04.140 --> 00:04:05.220
Brother.

00:04:06.520 --> 00:04:08.360
You are my only relative, you know?

00:04:09.360 --> 00:04:11.800
Do what you want but put your health first.

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:42.660
Hello!

00:04:56.600 --> 00:04:58.420
Actually, I'm also your boss, little brother.

00:04:59.620 --> 00:05:00.980
Who is your brother? 

00:05:03.640 --> 00:05:05.660
