00:05:12.880 --> 00:05:13.620
How is it?

00:05:21.840 --> 00:05:24.480
Okay, fine. I'm sorry.

00:05:27.520 --> 00:05:28.820
But, tell me.

00:05:29.500 --> 00:05:31.720
