00:05:50.420 --> 00:05:51.880
Mess around somewhere else!

00:05:52.100 --> 00:05:53.120
So annoying!

00:05:56.300 --> 00:05:58.520
Hey boy! Come here!

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:03.520
Your boss is calling you.

00:06:07.740 --> 00:06:09.260
He can't even remember my name!

00:06:16.080 --> 00:06:17.100
What is it?

00:06:19.620 --> 00:06:22.000
Even a child knows how to use subjects and predicates.

00:06:22.500 --> 00:06:25.340
Do you have a goldfish brain? You can't even remember my name!

00:06:28.660 --> 00:06:29.740
What's your name?

00:06:29.880 --> 00:06:30.760
Oh gosh!

00:06:30.940 --> 00:06:32.540
