00:06:35.340 --> 00:06:36.080
Okay!

00:06:36.340 --> 00:06:37.400
Just keep it that way!

00:06:37.580 --> 00:06:39.340
Maybe tomorrow there will be tons of ones

00:06:39.340 --> 00:06:40.540
who will take your orders!

00:06:40.980 --> 00:06:43.720
You're the most perverse one. There's no the second one. 

00:06:43.720 --> 00:06:44.960
Who's perverse?

00:06:50.380 --> 00:06:52.240
Why did you keep throwing it carelessly?

00:06:56.340 --> 00:06:58.560
Did you take all of them at once?

00:06:58.720 --> 00:07:00.000
Are you crazy?

00:07:02.480 --> 00:07:03.620
Open your mouth!

00:07:05.060 --> 00:07:06.500
I can't see anything.

00:07:06.580 --> 00:07:08.480
Spit it out! Spit!

00:07:12.680 --> 00:07:13.840
You like me, don't you?

00:07:16.980 --> 00:07:18.400
You're overconfident!

00:07:19.480 --> 00:07:21.240
I am never wrong.

00:07:22.280 --> 00:07:23.900
Now you are!

00:07:32.480 --> 00:07:33.360
"Thump."

00:07:33.760 --> 00:07:34.820
"Thump!"

00:07:35.340 --> 00:07:36.300
"Thump."

00:07:36.800 --> 00:07:37.720
"Thump!"

00:07:42.240 --> 00:07:43.720
Do you have any words to justify that?

00:07:45.000 --> 00:07:45.820
Hey!

00:07:46.100 --> 00:07:48.660
If you weren't my boss, I would have punched you in the face!

00:07:50.320 --> 00:07:52.060
Self-overconfidence can lead to self-killing!

00:08:04.400 --> 00:08:05.500
Open the door!

00:08:08.720 --> 00:08:09.980
Open it!

00:08:12.100 --> 00:08:13.060
Phuc!

00:08:14.700 --> 00:08:16.000
You remembered my name now, huh?

00:08:16.180 --> 00:08:17.660
But I won't do that!

00:08:23.220 --> 00:08:24.720
Open the door.

00:08:28.760 --> 00:08:29.980
Open it!

00:08:33.960 --> 00:08:34.940
Phuc!

00:08:38.180 --> 00:08:39.660
Why's he so quiet?

00:08:45.020 --> 00:08:46.220
Are... Are you okay?

00:08:50.920 --> 00:08:52.560
Why did you suddenly fall?

00:08:53.400 --> 00:08:54.660
It's your fault!

00:08:54.940 --> 00:08:56.080
Why was it my fault?

00:08:56.580 --> 00:08:57.860
Why did you close the door?

00:08:58.220 --> 00:09:00.520
I was polite! I had to close it when I went out!

00:09:00.620 --> 00:09:02.680
But we don't, in this house. Got it?

00:09:03.020 --> 00:09:03.640
No.

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:06.580
This kid!

00:09:07.780 --> 00:09:09.300
What happened to your legs?

00:09:09.600 --> 00:09:11.260
You look extremely pale with the pain!

00:09:15.260 --> 00:09:16.840
I haven't done anything!

00:09:19.460 --> 00:09:20.640
I'm okay.

00:09:20.760 --> 00:09:23.120
Hey! Don't think I'm gentle that you can bully me!

00:09:23.640 --> 00:09:25.500
I'm sorry. Okay?

00:09:49.780 --> 00:09:51.860
I can make soup with your legs.

00:09:52.720 --> 00:09:53.880
Not funny.

00:09:55.600 --> 00:09:58.000
Hey, do you have any therapy

00:09:58.200 --> 00:09:59.300
or take pills?

00:10:00.180 --> 00:10:02.200
I think you can't underestimate this.

00:10:04.380 --> 00:10:05.800
You don't need to care about it.

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:08.000
Will you die if someone cares about you?

00:10:08.080 --> 00:10:10.180
Yes. I'll die of shame.

00:10:21.460 --> 00:10:22.620
What happened, brother?

00:10:25.220 --> 00:10:26.340
I'm fine.

00:10:28.820 --> 00:10:30.260
Why do you have to hide it?

00:10:31.920 --> 00:10:33.500
You should get physical therapy.

00:10:33.960 --> 00:10:35.400
You can't leave it for too long.

00:10:35.580 --> 00:10:37.100
Now, you're on an outsider's side?

00:10:38.380 --> 00:10:41.320
Hey! Can you say something less harsh?

00:10:44.220 --> 00:10:46.720
Whatever you say, I won't agree with that.

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:53.980
I'm not a busybody,

00:10:54.240 --> 00:10:56.980
but I can't just stand there and see you dying.

00:11:05.900 --> 00:11:07.220
Try to stand as usual!

00:11:07.340 --> 00:11:08.320
Trust yourself.

00:11:08.540 --> 00:11:09.600
It's okay.

00:11:22.820 --> 00:11:24.300
Put the stick away.

00:11:25.160 --> 00:11:26.400
Let me hold it.

00:11:27.300 --> 00:11:28.440
