00:11:30.660 --> 00:11:32.120
Won't you steal my stick? 

00:11:32.540 --> 00:11:34.380
Do I look like I will need that?

00:11:35.100 --> 00:11:36.420
You think I can look?

00:11:37.460 --> 00:11:39.580
I mean that I'm an honest person.

00:11:39.680 --> 00:11:40.980
Give it to me.

00:12:04.800 --> 00:12:05.580
Okay.

00:12:06.100 --> 00:12:06.980
Very good.

00:12:09.580 --> 00:12:10.720
You can do it.

00:12:20.900 --> 00:12:22.180
I don't want to do it.

00:12:22.640 --> 00:12:23.760
What's wrong?

00:12:23.840 --> 00:12:25.420
You're doing well!

00:12:25.580 --> 00:12:26.860
You call that walking?

00:12:27.700 --> 00:12:29.420
