00:12:31.840 --> 00:12:34.300
There's no one who's both blind and lame!

00:12:38.920 --> 00:12:39.840
You tell me.

00:12:41.120 --> 00:12:43.100
You can't heal something that is already broken!

00:12:50.920 --> 00:12:52.500
You know nothing!

00:12:53.740 --> 00:12:55.340
You all know nothing!

00:12:55.760 --> 00:12:57.560
I understand what you're feeling.

00:12:57.880 --> 00:13:00.500
But you won't know if you don't try.

00:13:01.380 --> 00:13:04.520
The key thing is to get up after you fall.

00:13:05.980 --> 00:13:07.500
I believe you can make it.

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:09.820
Just stand up.

00:13:16.180 --> 00:13:17.280
Please stand up.

00:13:17.980 --> 00:13:18.700
I told you...

00:13:18.700 --> 00:13:19.920
I believe you can do it.

00:13:22.580 --> 00:13:23.840
Stand up, brother.

00:13:26.120 --> 00:13:27.560
Just need to stand up.

00:13:33.580 --> 00:13:36.400
Get your hands off me. I can do this.

00:14:49.600 --> 00:14:50.740
Is that you, Duy?

00:14:51.280 --> 00:14:52.380
Yes.

00:15:09.900 --> 00:15:10.880
It's for you.

00:15:20.440 --> 00:15:22.380
