00:15:26.660 --> 00:15:27.520
Sign it.

00:15:27.740 --> 00:15:29.180
It's all yours now.

00:15:31.040 --> 00:15:32.780
No, I won't!

00:15:34.780 --> 00:15:35.720
What's wrong?

00:15:35.920 --> 00:15:36.940
Don't want it?

00:15:37.600 --> 00:15:38.940
There'll be so much pressure.

00:15:39.140 --> 00:15:40.580
I want to work with relaxation.

00:15:48.680 --> 00:15:51.400
Don't worry. You'll get better soon.

00:15:53.960 --> 00:15:55.260
When is that?

00:15:57.440 --> 00:16:00.180
Trust me. Everything will be okay.

00:16:00.880 --> 00:16:05.020
Now, just leave it to me. I'll take care of it.

00:16:08.040 --> 00:16:10.300
Okay. Follow your words

00:16:14.420 --> 00:16:15.340
Brother,

00:16:16.460 --> 00:16:19.160
no matter it is for me, or it is for you,

00:16:19.880 --> 00:16:22.000
