00:16:46.840 --> 00:16:50.040
Who do you mean to a sick one? You're in good health.

00:16:52.780 --> 00:16:54.280
Am I not a sick person?

00:16:55.940 --> 00:17:00.580
You can walk, speak, and eat normally.

00:17:01.180 --> 00:17:02.880
You're very strong.

00:17:03.900 --> 00:17:06.540
Stop being insecure or anxious about yourself.

00:17:08.540 --> 00:17:11.760
Your life is still better than so many people's.

00:17:14.120 --> 00:17:17.500
I believe that, one day, you can regain your sight.

00:17:20.320 --> 00:17:23.020
At that moment, I want to see you.

00:17:26.980 --> 00:17:31.060
